ivardefs.name: category
ivardefs.desc: Dental, Vision, Medical, Pharmacy, Rehab etc.

ivardefs.name: description
ivardefs.desc: A richer description of the benefit, for example 'DENT2 covers 100% of basic, 50% of major but exclused Ortho, Implants and Costmetic services'.

ivardefs.name: excluded
ivardefs.desc: True if the indicated class of service is excluded from the plan, missing or False indicated the service is included in the coverage.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: A short name or tag for the benefit, for example MED01, or DENT2.

ivardefs.name: subCategory
ivardefs.desc: Dental: basic, major, ortho; Vision exam, glasses, contacts; etc.

ivardefs.name: term
ivardefs.desc: The term or period of the values such as 'maximum lifetime benefit' or 'maximum annual vistis'.

properties.desc: Benefits and optionally current balances by Category.
